                <li><span class="font-semibold">Deltion College - Software Developer @ ICT-Flex </span><span class="italic">[09-2021 - CURRENT]</span><br>At the time of writing this I am attending my second MBO study at Deltion College in Zwolle. My study is called Software Developer and it's given under a special department at Deltion called ICT-Flex. We're learning how to create, normalize and with with SQL databases, how to write a solid back-end using PHP and Laravel & how to write a good front-end using JS among other things. Other classes include Linux, Security & Project Management.</li>
