                <li><span class="font-semibold">Landstede MBO </span><span class="italic">[12-2020 - 07-2021]</span><br>My second internship was at Landstede MBO. Here I took up the role of IT assistant. I helped teachers and students with IT-related problems. For clarity: I wasn't an IT manager or anything. I did nothing related to AD or maintaining the school network. Instead I was tasked with on-site inspections and being a contactperson for IT-related questions. Activities include installing and updating computers within our network, helping people with miscellaneous issues such as internet connection not working, windows crashing and giving advice. I did this at two locations: Rechterland 1 and Rieteweg 12.</li>
